    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that feels like such a lie. like, how does \"making a positive impact\" matter when the whole system is fundamentally broken? it's like trying to put a band-aid on a gunshot wound. it just feels exhausting to keep fighting for a future that isn't even going to exist for us. it feels like we're just delaying the inevitable.",
