      "content": "i don't know. i just feel so heavy all the time. it's like, why bother even being here to witness the collapse? everything is just going to be taken away anyway. it feels more honest to just admit that it's all hopeless and stop pretending there's a way out. it would be so much easier to just not have to deal with this anymore.",
